# Restitution Principle
#
# When a party breaches a contract or wrongfully benefits, they have an obligation
# to restore the other party to their original position.
#
# Usage: apply restitution(Breach, Restoration)
#
# Legal Basis: Equitable remedy in contract law and unjust enrichment doctrine.

principle restitution(Breach, Restoration) {
    restoration_obligation = Breach implies oblig(Restoration)
}

